Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝贺你 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过感觉好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前些日子还在上学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同年级的同学大多升学了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军队里也有同样的课程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 父亲说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在需要我作为高达机师去宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 又要被周围人说是特殊待遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到罗玛丽也参军了 真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲 凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝贺你 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太公公别提多高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得打电话回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 你一定会没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成为独当一面的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为明日野家族的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是亚瑟姆·明日野？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫阿莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一样 是倍受期待的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么认识我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听传闻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日野司令官的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,享受特别待遇驾驶高达的少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道 习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老爸也是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和明日野司令官是老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 你老爸和我老爸是铁哥们儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们也得好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起加油吧 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和这艘船真有缘分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的情况是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎启动 5分钟后各部门准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜蕾丝舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰接到机密物资运送任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经由 巨环基地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往 奥利巴诺兹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加紧准备出航
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球吗 第一次去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？ 我去过喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽 你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽 你为什么参军？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 完全没那种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从小很听爸爸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 突然找到了想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么非要是联邦军？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实另有缘由吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持安静
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中精力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手 别动嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基地司令官专用飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日野司令官按预定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先于本舰前往巨环基地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大排场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨环基地司令官有战舰护航
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是今天起正式就任达乌内斯司令官的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特·葛雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么年轻的司令官？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为那种家伙卖命？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然宣布这么年轻的人是司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会这样也无可厚非
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难免有人嫉妒你的年龄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗 元气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,元气 元气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是高达？怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙 可以根据情况需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从飞行状态变形成人形状态
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是AGE系统设计出的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达二代机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达AGE-2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达… AGE-2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯老爷子根据你以往的战斗数据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最新制造出的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙上面装备的高能多兹步枪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有原来两倍的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等AGE系统的微调工作完成后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就能上战场了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的高达呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达AGE在巨环基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成和AGE系统的分离作业后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会改装成独立机型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 新人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士展览会结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员集合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我也得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达今后由我这个主任机械工程师负责
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪克·甘海尔 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.14,0:10:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 都到齐了没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是 歌姬号机动战士队队长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫·安尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说军队上层对他避之不及
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次乱驾驶高达的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 性格像极了你爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当年和你爸一起打仗很带劲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长认识我父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们给我听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天起我就是你们的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战场上我的命令是绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白没？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说在沃尔夫队长手下干
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多少条命也不够
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 以前外号好像叫白狼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是军队里的王牌机师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白狼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不知道怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在沃尔夫队长手下干过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他虽不是军人的楷模
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却是最棒的队长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫队长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲以前就是那个样子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无懈可击 考虑周道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时确实是个有意思的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲是 有意思的小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸是谁不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和其他人同样是个兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油别让高达给人抢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出航准备完成 全员就位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号 慢速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取道 巨环基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,载有高达的联邦战舰开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是歌姬号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试探下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令摩挲·兰古力部队强行侦查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,载有高达的舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 你也在上面吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索敌系统有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士机影 6
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对照维甘机体数据
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员战斗配置…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们知道这艘船上装着高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对照完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘机动战士 多拉多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士队 紧急出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即进入迎击态势
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫少校出击 别磨磨蹭蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再凶一点就像欧巴桑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到没 沃尔夫队的初阵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前我说几句
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得新人加入 又多了虐待的乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住 全部给我活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕是抱着操纵杆飘回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的战斗 不是模拟战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊 保佑我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么高达无法出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 微调很费时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再等5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以 必须出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没空等高达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫队 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥布莱特·洛伦 杰诺亚斯-2 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莉莎·甘海尔 阿黛尔2号机出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克斯·哈特维 阿黛尔1号机出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫·安尼克 G-巨人出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩挲·兰古力 即将与敌接火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看他们的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是 战场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莉莎 走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们镇静点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细瞄准就会打中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细瞄准打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快 大家已经进入战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照例还要对机动战士形态进行扫描
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那时间了 马上出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,G强击模式 出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入战斗宇域前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用强击模式 移动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这形态有平时3倍的推进力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达 让我们一起去赢取生存
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆·明日野 AGE-2高达 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来晚了 沃尔夫队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟到的好好干活补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛮不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:19:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 这样没法出手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 还好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,状态终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是沃尔夫队长…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白狼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看清位置关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的射击线路上有歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运气不好的话 会直接击中歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙去歌姬号了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥布莱特 麦克斯和阿莉莎拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两台多拉多 接近歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达距离太近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 离开歌姬号射线轴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆上士 这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达AGE-2 击毁两台多拉多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙 一枪两个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部击落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 照顾完老的又是小的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩挲·兰古力部队全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击毁其中大半的是新型高达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新型？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是抗命行为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我把敌人干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军队里命令是绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无视指挥官的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让舰船暴露在危险之中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 毕竟是初阵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许插嘴 沃尔夫少校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍后再追究你的监督失责
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆·明日野上士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次命令下达前 寝室禁闭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须明白 要为自己的行为负责
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宽宏大量点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人不会把他当孩子对待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 这话不错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被训惨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.55,0:22:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放心上 你干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时完全忘我了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------EDCN2------------------------------------
