Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.48,0:24:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 机动战士高达AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.82,0:24:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色机动战士
